# Project structure

- **Package manager:** bun (`bun install`, `bun run` from **`web/`**); commit `bun.lock`.
- **App:** `web/src` — Next.js App Router; actions in `web/src/actions/`.
- **Routes:** `(root)/` · `(store)/[storeId]/` · `(auth)/` · `storeAdmin/` · `sysAdmin/` · `admin/` · `api/`.
- **Naming:** kebab-case routes; PascalCase components; shadcn in `components/ui`; colocate page components.
- Server pages fetch inline; SWR in nested clients; `"use client"` for interactivity; `"use server"` on action modules that export actions.
- **Repo:** `bin/`, `doc/` at root. See `AGENTS.md` for agent workflow.
